cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CE 

The paper discusses the use of signal processing and machine learning in the context of radiomics, which involves extracting features from medical images for predictive and prognostic models. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of electronic medical record keeping and communication systems, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the potential for personalized treatment, which could fall under computer engineering (cs.CE).
